{"tid":1227621,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"少數族裔定有少數族裔frd嘅都唔該入嚟！一齊share呢個聯署出去！","createTime":"2019-06-15T15:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T06:22:23.000Z","uid":89690,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9866653f616b9b17001c4f8a1e66bad20ea1dff2","tid":1227621,"uid":89690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:23:13.000Z","msg":"各位連登巴絲：<br />\n<br />\n香港嘅少數族裔都有留意近日發生嘅事情，知道政府葫蘆裏面賣咩毒藥，知道呢個家再唔守護就會冇。我哋當中有人係土生土長，有人係移民過嚟，但我哋都同樣熱愛呢片土地。同其他香港人一樣，我哋有去遊行示威、同香港人一齊搏命。我哋希望可以同大家並肩作戰去守護呢個家，守護呢個屬於大家嘅香港。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家身邊有任何少數族裔嘅朋友，都懇請你哋share呢條聯署link俾佢哋。Share得一個得一個，令我哋嘅聲音都可以受到關注。<br />\n<br />\n生於亂世，大家都有種責任！香港人，聽日見！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/YcjKSyYJ2RKjt86K6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FYcjKSyYJ2RKjt86K6&d=1pbl5WvK8XMTdm%2FDcZs%2FeJLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=d980c2a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/YcjKSyYJ2RKjt86K6</a>"},{"pid":"d972ddfe2ed06cf7d47d4df68332d6081e473a02","tid":1227621,"uid":259446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:27:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf9d1dc41a6ac9809a12ed70ceb64378eb5068b","tid":1227621,"uid":259446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:34:03.000Z","msg":"記得些牙出去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b3b2558849e1edd637332269152e7dd8465c6b0","tid":1227621,"uid":259446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:41:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69fcb5d619ddcc033670caba25a2a1b353fe0af","tid":1227621,"uid":259446,"like":0,"d